Eleven-year experience with tibiotibial bypass: an unusual but effective 
solution to distal tibial artery occlusive disease and limited autologous vein.

Lyon RT(1), Veith FJ, Marsan BU, Wengerter KR, Panetta TF, Marin ML, Goldsmith 
J, Rivers SP, Suggs W.

Author information:
(1)Montefiore Medical Center, Albert Einstein College of Medicine, Bronx, New 
